\displaystyle \lim_{n \to \infty} \int_0^\infty \frac{e^{-x}\cos{x}}{nx^2 + \frac{1}{n}}dx
 \lim_{n \to \infty} \int_0^{\infty} \frac{e^{-x} \cos x}{nx^2+1/n}\,dx = \int_{0}^{\infty} \frac{dy}{y^2+1} = \frac{\pi}{2}. 
\forall n\in Z^+\forall x\geq 1[x^2+1\leq nx^2+\frac{1}{n}]
\forall n\in Z^+\forall x\geq1[\frac{e^{-x}\cos{x}}{nx^2 + \frac{1}{n}}\leq\frac{e^{-x}\cos{x}}{x^2 + 1}]
